{"tid":732642,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"點解劉嗚偉講咩 都有位比連登/記者插?","createTime":"2018-07-07T05:41:03.000Z","updateTime":"2020-05-12T03:53:43.000Z","uid":125663,"like":3,"dislike":65,"uniUserReply":25,"replies":[{"pid":"9d6a7c5324535c0667df3dec53d1f916e9844b27","tid":732642,"uid":125663,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-07T05:41:03.000Z","msg":"拿, 之前佢話 去少幾次日本  每個月草$3000 上樓  又比連登仔同記者插 , 話佢太離地<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.lifestyle.appledaily.com/lifestyle/columnist/daily/article/20180626/20431253\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.lifestyle.appledaily.com%2Flifestyle%2Fcolumnist%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20180626%2F20431253&d=zrTRZ2mwaJxZQo0%2B%2FKHujY9%2BoveFa0K0Z8Wn6wXPu4k%3D&h=f9089361\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.lifestyle.appledaily.com%2Flifestyle%2Fcolumnist%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20180626%2F20431253&h=9778b1bf\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.lifestyle.appledaily.com/lifestyle/columnist/daily/article/20180626/20431253</a><br />\n而家呢單評論,  劉嗚偉話 : &quot;讀大學不要期望變中產&quot;  。 呢句無離地啦掛? 記者都認同劉生講得岩, 反映到現實情況. <br />\n<br />\n但做咩係都要再插佢幾句講：&quot;劉公子儘管說得對，但出自他的嘴巴，大家總覺得難聽過粗口。他一站出來，什麼也不必說，已道成肉身地展示一個社會現實：苦幹不如父幹。建議劉公子改善一下溝通技巧，不是每句真心話都應該講的，比如我說「做大劉嘅仔，都唔好期望得到爸爸全副身家」，也是事實，但勵志嗎？&quot;  <br />\n<br />\n屌, 離地又比人屌, 唔離地講社會事實又比人屌.  你地想佢點? 想佢一句聲都唔撚出?"},{"pid":"24fd794e6fc971f2adaf39c73d6b94736380f11b","tid":732642,"uid":57835,"like":33,"dislike":0,"score":33,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-07T05:42:11.000Z","msg":"佢既離地係假膠級數"},{"pid":"c0bf8516a56776001370535af36e949cc8b9da00","tid":732642,"uid":89931,"like":23,"dislike":0,"score":23,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-07T05:46:37.000Z","msg":"因為香港唔需要有劉鳴煒嘅存在<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/censored.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"37ba4c29a5a64ac7bc5d22a5d269613408a9ef1c","tid":732642,"uid":125663,"like":2,"dislike":21,"score":-19,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-07T05:48:13.000Z","msg":"劉生佢離地 去少幾次日本呢個言論 我見到都好嬲.<br />\n但佢今次話 讀大學 唔好期望變中產  in gen